    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition and has been consistently well-maintained. The exterior displays a healthy shine, though upon closer inspection, you will find some minor stone chips on the hood and a few light surface scratches consistent with careful daily use. Inside, the cabin is clean and free of major wear, with all electronics and climate controls functioning as they should. It drives smoothly and has a solid service history, making it a reliable choice for its next owner.",
