      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "We are pleased to present this distinguished vehicle, a testament to consistent maintenance and mechanical integrity. This example showcases a well-preserved exterior and a refined interior environment, reflecting a history of attentive ownership. Engineered for those who demand reliability and performance, the vehicle has undergone a comprehensive inspection to ensure it meets our professional standards. It offers a sophisticated driving experience and represents a high-value acquisition for the discerning motorist seeking a dependable, high-caliber automobile.",
      "price": 34900.0,
