    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty ride, and honestly, it\u2019s been such a joy to drive. It's in really solid shape and has been super well-taken care of over the years. Whether you're heading to work or planning a weekend getaway, this car is totally ready for the road! It runs smooth, looks great, and I\u2019ve made sure it\u2019s always kept up to date. I\u2019d love to see it go to someone who will enjoy it as much as I have. Drop me a message if you want to take it for a spin!",
      "price": 33800.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 32
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This 2004 Porsche 911 Carrera 4S (996.2) features the iconic wide-body silhouette and integrated rear reflector strip. Powered by a 3.6L M96 flat-six with VarioCam Plus, it delivers linear power through a precise 6-speed manual transaxle and an advanced viscous-clutch AWD system. The chassis benefits from factory-upgraded suspension and cross-drilled rotors clamped by four-piston monoblock calipers. This example presents in strong mechanical health, with a documented IMS bearing retrofit and a firm clutch take-up. The hydraulic steering remains communicative and unweighted, offering the pure analog feedback enthusiasts demand.",
      "price": 36500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 32
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Used car. Good condition. Well maintained. Clean title. Minor cosmetic wear. Mechanically sound.",
      "price": 28500.0,
